About Us
Indian River RV Park campground is conveniently walking distance to CVS, grocery store, retail, restaurants, art galleries, local brewery and much much more. You can enjoy rocket launches, sunrises and cool breezes off the Indian River from our quaint historical downtown location. We are nestled with canopy of many trees and lots of shade for cool comfort. Titusville’s Class A Motorhome secret Class A RV Resort Campground Titusville Florida on the Indian River. You will be minutes from local pristine beaches, Kennedy Space Center, Cape Canaveral, Cocoa Beach, Daytona Beach, Orlando Florida Disney World and Universal Studio’s theme parks. Make sure to bring your sunscreen, sunglasses, fishing poles, kayak’s, bicycles and beach gear. We provide wireless internet at no extra charge. Happy Campers Welcome! Front row seats to the rocket launches.
